infra.name: te0808_2es2
infra.description: Zynq UltraScale+ TE0808-2ES2 Board (form factor 5.2x7.6 cm) with 4x 512 MByte DDR4, Speed Grade -2 and industrial temperature range. Supported PCB Revisions: REV03, REV04. Board Part is only with minimum PS-Setup. Use for own carrier or simple SDK debugging. User must configure B2B MIOs manually, depending on his carrier board connection. Without user PS configuration only JTAG and QSPI boot is possible with this board part file.
infra.author: trenz.biz
